cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|Obviously the 2N ^*Bis not Unusual 2N^*N. If I were 5/5 in the minors, I would have bid 2N over 1@S. If I had a strong NT, I would have bid 1N over 1S. So my 2N can be neither of those. My 2N bid is takeout for the minors. In a pinch, I could even be 4/4 in the minors although 5/4 is more common. I do not want to let them play in 2@S, as you know. |
