cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|While it is true you should be more conservative, in general, other than some very rare borderline hands, vulnerability has very little effect on when you balance. Most people do not balance when they should, and this just gives them another excuse to make a bad decision not to balance. Bottom line is, vulnerability is a minor factor at best in deciding whether or not to balance.|
